          <attvalue for="1" value="A DYNAMIC MODEL OF GROWTH PHASES AND SURVIVAL IN INTERNATIONAL BUSINESS-TO-BUSINESS NEW VENTURES: THE MODERATING EFFECT OF DECISION-MAKING LOGIC" />
