      <node id="RAHIMI A, 2026, J HOSP LEIS SPORT TO" label="RAHIMI A, 2026, J HOSP LEIS SPORT TO">
        <attvalues>
          <attvalue for="0" value="true" />
          <attvalue for="1" value="ENTREPRENEURIAL MARKETING EDUCATION AND INTENTIONS IN SPORT: INVESTIGATING THE MODERATING EFFECT OF SPORTING CAPITAL" />
          <attvalue for="2" value="RAHIMI A;GANDOMANI RA;SHAHBAZPOUR L;KHANYOURDI MN;HASANZADEH N" />
          <attvalue for="3" value="AMIR RAHIMI; ROHOLLAH ASGARI GANDOMANI; LEILA SHAHBAZPOUR; MEYSAM NOORI KHANYOURDI; NIMA HASANZADEH" />
          <attvalue for="4" value="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4851-150X; NO ORCID; NO ORCID; NO ORCID; NO ORCID" />
          <attvalue for="5" value="AS SPORT INCREASINGLY INTERSECTS WITH ENTREPRENEURSHIP, UNDERSTANDING HOW SPORT STUDENTS TRANSLATE ENTREPRENEURIAL LEARNING INTO INTENTION BECOMES A PRESSING ACADEMIC AND PRACTICAL CONCERN. THIS STUDY EXPLORES THE EXTENT TO WHICH ENTREPRENEURIAL MARKETING EDUCATION (EME) SHAPES ENTREPRENEURIAL INTENTIONS (EI) AMONG SPORT SCIENCE STUDENTS, FOCUSING ON TWO KEY COGNITIVE PREDICTORS: PERCEIVED DESIRABILITY (PD) AND PERCEIVED FEASIBILITY (PF). DRAWING ON A NATIONAL SAMPLE OF 435 UNDERGRADUATES ACROSS IRANIAN UNIVERSITIES, STRUCTURAL EQUATION MODELING REVEALED THAT EME SIGNIFICANTLY ENHANCES BOTH PD AND PF-THOUGH NOT ALL PEDAGOGICAL ELEMENTS CONTRIBUTED EQUALLY. WHAT ELEVATES THIS RESEARCH IS ITS REVELATION OF SPORTING CAPITAL (SC) AS A DECISIVE MODERATING FORCE. CONCEPTUALIZED AS A MULTIDIMENSIONAL BLEND OF PHYSICAL ABILITY, PSYCHOLOGICAL RESILIENCE, AND SOCIAL CONNECTIVITY, SC NOT ONLY AMPLIFIES THE EFFECT OF EME, BUT DOES SO MORE POWERFULLY AMONG FEMALE STUDENTS-WHERE IT APPEARS TO COUNTERBALANCE STRUCTURAL AND CULTURAL BARRIERS THROUGH EMBODIED CONFIDENCE AND SOCIAL REINFORCEMENT. THESE FINDINGS REFRAME ENTREPRENEURSHIP EDUCATION AS A LIVED, CONTEXT-SENSITIVE PROCESS SHAPED NOT ONLY BY COGNITIVE FACTORS BUT BY SPORT-ROOTED EXPERIENCES. THEORETICALLY, THIS STUDY BRIDGES ENTREPRENEURIAL COGNITION WITH EMBODIED CAPITAL; PRACTICALLY, IT CALLS FOR LEARNING ENVIRONMENTS THAT ACTIVATE THE PHYSICAL, EMOTIONAL, AND RELATIONAL STRENGTHS OF SPORT STUDENTS IN PURSUIT OF ENTREPRENEURIAL FUTURES." />
          <attvalue for="6" value="2026.0" />
          <attvalue for="7" value="JOURNAL OF HOSPITALITY LEISURE SPORT &amp; TOURISM EDUCATION" />
          <attvalue for="8" value="J HOSP LEIS SPORT TO" />
          <attvalue for="9" value="IRAN; IRAN; IRAN; IRAN" />
          <attvalue for="10" value="10.1016/j.jhlste.2026.100598" />
          <attvalue for="11" value="10.1016/j.jhlste.2026.100598" />
        </attvalues>
      </node>
