        <attvalues>
          <attvalue for="0" value="true" />
          <attvalue for="1" value="THE EFFECT OF A MARKET ORIENTATION, ENTREPRENEURIAL ORIENTATION, AND TECHNOLOGICAL CAPABILITY ON INNOVATIVENESS: A STUDY OF YOUNG BIOTECHNOLOGY VENTURES IN THE UNITED STATES AND IN SCANDINAVIA" />
