          <attvalue for="2" value="HAIR J.F.; RINGLE C.M.; SARSTEDT M." />
          <attvalue for="3" value="JOE F. HAIR; CHRISTIAN M. RINGLE; MARKO SARSTEDT" />
          <attvalue for="4" value="; HTTPS://ORCID.ORG/0000-0002-7027-8804; HTTPS://ORCID.ORG/0000-0002-5424-4268" />
          <attvalue for="5" value="DEAR COLLEAGUES:OVER THE PAST DECADE OR SO, THE FIELD OF MANAGEMENT HAS WITNESSED THE RISE OF PSYCHOLOGICAL OWNERSHIP AS AN IMPORTANT INDIVIDUAL-LEVEL PREDICTOR OF WORKPLACE MOTIVES, ATTITUDES, AND..." />
          <attvalue for="6" value="2011.0" />
          <attvalue for="7" value="THE JOURNAL OF MARKETING THEORY AND PRACTICE" />
