      <node id="BERNAL S, 2002, INT J ENTREP BEHAV RES" label="BERNAL S, 2002, INT J ENTREP BEHAV RES">
        <attvalues>
          <attvalue for="0" value="true" />
          <attvalue for="1" value="COMPETITOR NETWORKS: INTERNATIONAL COMPETITIVENESS THROUGH COLLABORATION" />
          <attvalue for="2" value="BERNAL S.M.H.; BURR C.; JOHNSEN R." />
          <attvalue for="3" value="SANDRA MARCELA HERRERA BERNAL; CAROLINE BURR; RHONA JOHNSEN" />
          <attvalue for="4" value="; ; HTTPS://ORCID.ORG/0000-0002-9574-3610" />
          <attvalue for="5" value="THE CASE OF THE GLOBAL FREIGHT FORWARDING INDUSTRY IS ONE EXAMPLE WHERE NETWORKS OF SMALL‐ TO MEDIUM‐SIZED ENTERPRISES (SMES) ARE PLAYING AN INCREASINGLY IMPORTANT ROLE. INTERNATIONALISATION OPPORTUNITIES AND COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGES MAY BE OBTAINED BY SMES IN POOLING THEIR RESOURCES AND EXCHANGING INFORMATION AND EXPERTISE. THIS EMPIRICAL CASE STUDY EXAMINES HORIZONTAL COLLABORATION BETWEEN SMES THAT CONSIDER THEIR OTHER NETWORK MEMBERS, FIRST AND FOREMOST, AS COMPETITORS." />
          <attvalue for="6" value="2002.0" />
          <attvalue for="7" value="INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ENTREPRENEURIAL BEHAVIOUR &amp; RESEARCH" />
          <attvalue for="8" value="INT J ENTREP BEHAV RES" />
          <attvalue for="9" value="" />
          <attvalue for="10" value="10.1108/13552550210448348" />
          <attvalue for="11" value="10.1108/13552550210448348" />
        </attvalues>
      </node>
