      <node id="LEHMAN K, 2020" label="LEHMAN K, 2020">
        <attvalues>
          <attvalue for="0" value="true" />
          <attvalue for="1" value="THE ROLE OF EFFECTUATION AND ENTREPRENEURIAL MARKETING IN THE CREATION OF A NEW ART VENTURE" />
          <attvalue for="2" value="LEHMAN K.; FILLIS I.; MILES M.P." />
          <attvalue for="3" value="KIM LEHMAN; IAN FILLIS; MORGAN P. MILES" />
          <attvalue for="4" value="HTTPS://ORCID.ORG/0000-0002-1652-4701; HTTPS://ORCID.ORG/0000-0002-8735-0948; HTTPS://ORCID.ORG/0000-0002-1389-1856" />
          <attvalue for="5" value="THE AUTHORS ANALYSE THE LITERATURE ON THE ROLES OF EFFECTUATION AND ENTREPRENEURIAL MARKETING IN NEW MARKET CREATION. THEY THEN ASSESS THE CONTRIBUTIONS OF EFFECTUATION IN THE MARKET CREATION ACTIVITIES. A SERIES OF RESEARCH QUESTIONS ARE CONSTRUCTED AND A CASE STUDY METHODOLOGY DEVELOPED WHERE THEY EVALUATE THE IMPACT OF EFFECTUAL LOGIC AND ENTREPRENEURIAL MARKETING ON THE CREATION OF AN INNOVATIVE NEW ART VENTURE. A LIMITED NUMBER OF CASE STUDIES HAVE BEEN UTILISED IN PREVIOUS EFFECTUATION RESEARCH AND THE AUTHORS BUILD ON THIS BY CONTEXTUALISING TO THE ARTS AND CULTURAL SECTOR. THEY MAKE A SERIES OF RECOMMENDATIONS FOR THEORY AND PRACTICE, INCLUDING THE IMPACT ON THE WIDER ARTS AND TOURISM INDUSTRY." />
          <attvalue for="6" value="2020.0" />
          <attvalue for="7" value="EDWARD ELGAR PUBLISHING EBOOKS" />
          <attvalue for="8" value="" />
          <attvalue for="9" value="" />
          <attvalue for="10" value="10.4337/9781785364570.00034" />
          <attvalue for="11" value="10.4337/9781785364570.00034" />
        </attvalues>
      </node>
