          <attvalue for="5" value="THIS STUDY INTRODUCES AND VALIDATES A MEASURE OF COUNTRY INSTITUTIONAL PROFILE FOR ENTREPRENEURSHIP CONSISTING OF REGULATORY, COGNITIVE, AND NORMATIVE DIMENSIONS. SUBSCALES BASED ON DATA FROM SIX C..." />
