          <attvalue for="5" value="THE ARTICLE DISCUSSES THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN ORGANIZATIONS AND THE ENVIRONMENT. THE STUDY EXAMINES WHETHER OR NOT INDUSTRY TYPE IS AN IMPORTANT VARIABLE IN THE TYPE OF UNCERTAINTY FELT BY EXECUTI..." />
